WEBVTT

00:00:41.133 --> 00:00:44.266 align:center position:50.00% line:9.86% size:57.00%
Ever wish someone would
sit on hold for you?

00:00:44.266 --> 00:00:45.266 align:center position:50.00% line:9.86% size:30.00%
iPhone will.

00:00:45.266 --> 00:00:47.333 align:center position:50.00% line:9.86% size:57.00%
Just press this button,
go do your thing,

00:00:47.333 --> 00:00:49.333 align:center position:50.00% line:9.86% size:72.00%
and you'll get a notification
when it's time to pick up.

